            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent-coral flex-shrink-0"></span>
                <span>Identified issues through testing and debug</span>
